snippet: Fallon Ellis scored a career-high 18 points, and unranked Iowa State stunned No. 3 Baylor, handing the Lady Bears their second straight loss after a 26-1 start.
abstract: Women's College Basketball Roundup; Iowa State defeats Baylor, 76-71; other women's college basketball scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Fallon Ellis scored a career-high 18 points, and unranked Iowa State stunned No. 3 Baylor, handing the Lady Bears their second straight loss after a 26-1 start.
